{"tid":1042480,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone Lightning 轉 3.5mm 耳機線 15 蚊平賣！用法竟然是「插完再藍牙再插」？","createTime":"2019-03-01T14:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T17:43:45.000Z","uid":51464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"235a1ea7ca15ae4357de4d04928c41a2a4c6aa66","tid":1042480,"uid":51464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:57:15.000Z","msg":"iPhone 的原廠配件售價較貴，很多人為了節省開支，普遍會改為購買副廠甚至「山寨」配件。最近深水埗電子特賣城亦有售 iPhone 專用的副廠 Lightning 轉 3.5mm 耳機線，售價只是 HK$15，跟售價為 HK$69 的原廠 Lightning 轉 3.5mm 耳機線相比，副廠售價只是原廠約兩折的水平。不過，副廠 Lightning 轉 3.5mm 耳機線並不可直接使用，需要以「插完再藍牙再插」方式使用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2283476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2283476&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=618604d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2283476</a><br />\n============================<br />\n「插完再藍牙再插」，一樓一新花式嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a459d286c8223d28db51e486aac0a886a7e2917","tid":1042480,"uid":30067,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"Lightning&gt;藍牙&gt;另一邊藍牙&gt;3.5mm"},{"pid":"27edbcafc4f49bf76efa4cca4cd2d8971d8467b1","tid":1042480,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:00:02.000Z","msg":"電子垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f89cce3721ab76ff81b7738a68b60b88d99eb0","tid":1042480,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"即係藍芽發射器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身都有藍芽啦"},{"pid":"3acf086bc2777b3706640856